$$
\boxed{
\begin{pmatrix}
G(a,q) = \left(\frac{a}{q}\right)\sqrt{q} \times \begin{cases} 1 & \text{若 } q \equiv 1 \pmod{4} \\ i & \text{若 } q \equiv 3 \pmod{4} \end{cases} \text{ (}q\text{ 为奇数)}
&
|G(a,q)| = \begin{cases} \sqrt{q} & \text{若 } q \text{ 为奇数} \\ 0 & \text{若 } q \equiv 2 \pmod{4} \\ \sqrt{2q} & \text{若 } q \equiv 0 \pmod{4} \end{cases}
\end{pmatrix}
}
$$
